entries.name: filename
entries.desc: The filename of the form data part

entries.name: name
entries.desc: The name of the form data part

entries.name: <<(str)
entries.desc: Adds str to this FormData which may be the body, a header or a header entry.

entries.name: [](*key)
entries.desc: Retrieves the header at the first entry in key

entries.name: append_data(data)
entries.desc: Adds data at the end of the chain of entries

entries.name: each_data()
entries.desc: Yields each entry in this FormData

entries.name: list()
entries.desc: Returns all the FormData as an Array

entries.name: to_ary()
entries.desc: A FormData will behave like an Array
